name: Wudup Orangu-Tank
description:
JPG 4000x4000px

Joining the celebration of #HEN500K Wudup is inviting a weird mecha bot inspired by old bill 500 Indonesian Rupiah, an Orangutan that transformed into a super robot named Orangu-Tank that will fight the deforestation in this world.

ABOUT WUDUP SERIES
Wudup is a series created by Artkelso (Ritchie Ned Hansel) presenting a repetition of his trademark character Mr. Chicken Bird. Here the series will be featured with guest stars that will appear on the right side of the artboards. Enjoy and don't have a good day, HAVE A GREAT DAY!
